# Server role tags — copy to .tag and list the roles that apply to this server.
# One tag per line. Available tags:
#
#   web       — HTTP (80) + HTTPS (443)
#   mail      — SMTP, POP3, IMAP (plain + SSL)
#   sip       — SIP signaling + RTP media streams
#   h323      — H.323 video conferencing
#   dns       — Authoritative DNS server
#   gateway   — NAT router / LAN gateway  (needs LAN1/LAN1_IP_RANGE in user/.env)
#   logging   — Log all dropped packets   (list LAST if used)
#
# Example for a web + mail server:
# web
# mail

web
